HEADWORD: Gamin
<hw>Gam"in</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F.]</ety> <def>A
neglected and untrained city boy; a young street Arab.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>In Japan, the <qex>gamins</qex> run after you, and say, 'Look at
the Chinaman.'</q> <rj><qau>L. Oliphant.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>gaminess</ent>⟦br⟧
